@startuml clipboard-clear-state-machine
title Clipboard Clear Task - State Machine From Use Cases

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1976D2
}

[*] --> NoPendingCopy

NoPendingCopy --> PendingClear : CopyEntryPasswordUseCase saves hash metadata\nand schedules clearClipboard
PendingClear --> PendingClear : CopyEntryPasswordUseCase clears/cancels previous task\nthen saves replacement task
PendingClear --> NoPendingCopy : ClearClipboardTaskUseCase clears matching clipboard value
PendingClear --> NoPendingCopy : clipboard changed, metadata removed by service
PendingClear --> PendingClear : stale action ignored
PendingClear --> PendingClear : requireExpired and not expired
PendingClear --> NoPendingCopy : LockVaultUseCase clears with requireExpired = false
PendingClear --> NoPendingCopy : schedule or clipboard write failure cleanup

note right of PendingClear
Pending metadata is actionId, copiedValueHash, expiresAt.
The plaintext password is only written to ClipboardPort.
end note

@enduml
